      },
      "time": "~20s",
      "narrative": "- The local proof of concept showed that the task works.\n- Now the agent needs to grow up.\n- Move into an environment with the security, governance, and visibility required for production use.",
      "demo_actions": "Transition from the local POC to VS Code or the enterprise build environment. Frame this as the move from experiment to production.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260622_142419_vlcsnap-2026-06-22-14h24m13s620.png"
