        "design_plan": true
      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "- In VS Code, connect the agent to the right IQs.\n- Make the data access explicit.\n- The POC used simulated records.\n- This version can reach real enterprise evidence.\n- Show the guardrails around what tools the agent can call and when.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the agent project in VS Code. Show configuration for IQs, tool access, or policy controls. Point to the guardrails on tool calls.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260622_142540_vlcsnap-2026-06-22-14h25m35s396.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": true,
      "locks": {
