        "narrative": true,
        "demo_actions": true,
        "screenshot": true,
        "visual": true,
        "design_plan": true
      },
      "time": "~35s",
      "narrative": "- Invoice assurance depends on more than the invoice itself.\n- The agent now has the right toolbox.\n- It can pull contracts, invoice records, receipts, batch records, quality status, milestone approvals, materials data, and capacity context into one review.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the toolbox or connected data sources. Walk through the evidence sources the agent can access.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260622_142437_vlcsnap-2026-06-22-14h24m33s324.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": true,
      "locks": {
