        "narrative": true,
        "demo_actions": true,
        "screenshot": true,
        "visual": true,
        "design_plan": true
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- Once connected, deploy the agent as a hosted agent in Foundry.\n- This gives us a managed runtime with isolation.\n- It also gives us a clear execution path we can inspect.\n- Just like MXC but in the cloud",
      "demo_actions": "Deploy the agent in Foundry. Show hosted agent setup, cloud isolation cues, and a simple execution.",
      "screenshot": ".cutready/screenshots/20260622_142605_vlcsnap-2026-06-22-14h25m58s345.png"
    },
    {
      "locked": true,
      "locks": {
