        "design_plan": true
      },
      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- Here is a simple interaction.\n- A user asks about an invoice.\n- The agent responds with a recommendation grounded in contract and operating evidence.\n- This is not just a free-form answer.",
      "demo_actions": "Run a short Teams interaction tied to invoice assurance. Ask the agent to review or explain an invoice decision and show the response.",
