      "time": "~30s",
      "narrative": "- Because this is now part of an enterprise environment, governance is visible.\n- Show approvals.\n- Show listing.\n- Show access.\n- Show auditability around the agent itself, not just its output.",
      "demo_actions": "Open the A365 governance view. Show approvals, listing, access controls, and audit trail or activity history.",
